{"tid":2491021,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"電騙案16人損失1.3億元 其中一人被騙6890萬元 有人承認以特務身份騙取款項","createTime":"2021-04-16T04:34:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T05:15:25.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4b6e2f944d1e6eef0242fd2862c852bc02a93721","tid":2491021,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:34:54.000Z","msg":"警方展開反電話騙案行動及宣傳活動，拘捕11人，涉及16受害者，總涉款金額達1億3000萬元，其中單一涉及最多騙款金額的案件達6890萬元。警方同時成功截取1200萬元的電騙款項，正追捕其他在逃人士。<br />\n<br />\n警方說，16宗案件當中，14宗騙案手法均為假冒官員，有人承認以特務身份騙取款項，亦有人自稱是電騙受害者，包括提供戶口，作不法用途。被騙去6890萬元的女受害人，60多歲，去年10月她乘搭港鐵回家途中收到電話，對方聲稱她在內地涉及洗黑錢案，要求將所有積蓄轉到銀行戶口。涉及這宗案件的找換店東主已被捕。<br />\n<br />\n11名被捕人士包括5男6女，16名受害者年齡介乎15歲至83歲，當中一人持雙程證來港。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，騙徒最短在兩日內成功騙取數十萬元，最長的案件持續70日，受害者當中的長者被騙走畢生積蓄，呼籲市民多些主動關心身邊長者。<br />\n<br />\n今年首季有200宗電騙，較上季下跌33%左右，但較去年同期上升18%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586116-20210416.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586116-20210416.htm&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLbHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=b7abee12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586116-20210416.htm&h=61c24272\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586116-20210416.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9a70775124134968fa63886e0524869f87176d53","tid":2491021,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:43:22.000Z","msg":"佢果6000 萬係咪老豆俾佢"},{"pid":"ff9431dcf4699122e2760515289a455ddc60e54a","tid":2491021,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:03:14.000Z","msg":"689<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5077065c746c8840924522defafc4dad1bb06c13","tid":2491021,"uid":52303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:05:09.000Z","msg":"唔怪得咁多電話騙案<br />\n咁多有錢傻佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成功一次都唔洗休"},{"pid":"0be1d95a2782260c0252ba0dd4f064336b089592","tid":2491021,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:05:28.000Z","msg":"又玩中國特務呢招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e955b61341b4912c235d9ee59a33354cc7650a7","tid":2491021,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:08:32.000Z","msg":"我試過接聽 之後佢cut我線<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該係睇你係咪操流利國語<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a6145ee2288f668ca00b082bd0a24830d04c05","tid":2491021,"uid":327169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:09:05.000Z","msg":"特務! <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbqJZhz1LDktDj7bayk4gUofWSSnWU1hFNgNkwoZwJ774?filename=vPA5zcv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvPA5zcv.jpg&h=52d857bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b074b5f379def259f28f12210fd213316714702f","tid":2491021,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5077065c746c8840924522defafc4dad1bb06c13","tid":2491021,"uid":52303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:05:09.000Z","msg":"唔怪得咁多電話騙案<br />\n咁多有錢傻佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成功一次都唔洗休"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:13:34.000Z","msg":"本身佢真係有喺大陸洗黑錢所以咪會信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74845f9cd85fee46c252b50824aa5bc4316a53b6","tid":2491021,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:15:25.000Z","msg":"係咪眞係身有屎"}]}